- Cheers!

74
00:10:38,450 --> 00:10:41,950
Cheers!
- Cheers!

75
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:48,050
Another round.

76
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:49,750
Umm...

77
00:10:49,850 --> 00:10:52,100
Your generosity ...

78
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:55,500
