87
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:36,050
We won't hear it.
We won't.

88
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:39,000
Let him sleep, Hamilton.
- Hm ...

89
00:12:39,100 --> 00:12:41,150
A good night's rest.

90
00:12:41,250 --> 00:12:43,850
And tomorrow...

91
00:12:44,050 --> 00:12:46,750
Tomorrow, tomorrow you will feel
as well and refreshed..

92
00:12:46,850 --> 00:12:48,750
As though the earth were new again.

93
00:12:48,850 --> 00:12:52,650
Hamilton! There's nothing more
we can do for him.

94
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:57,200
Such is the pity.

95
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:08,450
Well, my boy,
