My name is Solomon Northup.

98
00:13:13,500 --> 00:13:14,550
I am a free man.

99
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:16,950
A resident of Saratoga, New York.

100
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:19,550
The residence also of my wife and children
who are equally free.

101
00:13:19,650 --> 00:13:21,700
And you have no right
whatsoever to detain me--

102
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:24,700
Yah not any free man.
- And I promise you

103
