122
00:17:02,900 --> 00:17:05,100
There ...

123
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:09,300
Tha's fine.

124
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:11,750
Tha's fine.

125
00:17:14,250 --> 00:17:17,050
Got no gratitude?

126
00:17:20,550 --> 00:17:23,650
No! It was from my wife.
- Rags and tatters.

127
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:27,150
Rags and tatters.

128
00:17:36,150 --> 00:17:39,350
Go on. Warsh up.

129
00:17:40,750 --> 00:17:44,250
The boy, too.
Get him clean.

130
00:17:45,150 --> 00:17:46,650
Scrub now.

131
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:49,500
Do you know when my Mama will come?

132
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:51,500
Hush him up!
- Mama! Mama!

133
00:17:51,600 --> 00:17:53,900
Quiet! Quiet.
- Mama!

134
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,800
Quiet! - Hush him up!
- Mama!

135
00:17:55,850 --> 00:17:59,650
Your mother will come, I swear she will,
but you must be silent.

136
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:02,150
Be silent!

137
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:10,800
We need a sympathetic ear.

138
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:12,700
An opportunity to explain our situation--

139
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:15,230
Who in your estimation
is that sympathetic ear?

140
00:18:15,256 --> 00:18:16,875
- The two men I journeyed with.

141
00:18:16,950 --> 00:18:18,950
I'm certain they're making inquires
at this very moment.

142
00:18:18,950 --> 00:18:20,496
I would be just as certain
they are counting the money,

143
00:18:20,522 --> 00:18:21,625
paid for delivering
you to this place.

144
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:24,150
They were not kidnappers.
They were artists.

145
00:18:24,250 --> 00:18:26,500
Fellow performers.
- You know that?

146
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:30,150
You know for certain who they were?

147
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:34,600
The reality to come is us
being transported southward.

148
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:37,300
New Orleans if I were to venture.

149
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:39,900
After we arrive, we'll be put to market.

150
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:42,500
And beyond that...

151
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:45,300
Well, once in a slave state
I suppose there's only one outcome.

152
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:45,900
No.

153
00:18:45,926 --> 00:18:47,925
- I don't say that to give
you empty agitation, John...

154
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:50,270
For y'all. For y'all they
ain't nothin' but that!

155
00:18:50,296 --> 00:18:51,475
But John was'n kidnapped.

156
00:18:51,550 --> 00:18:54,050
John bein' hold as debt, tha's all.

157
00:18:54,150 --> 00:18:56,050
Massa pay his debt,
and John be redeemed--

158
00:18:56,150 --> 00:18:59,100
Boy, our masters will not come for us.
- Now John's... John's sorry for y'all,

159
00:18:59,150 --> 00:19:03,800
but tha's how it be.
Where y'all goin', yah goin' witout John.

160
