Mama!
- Randall.

161
00:19:06,650 --> 00:19:09,550
Mama!

162
00:19:09,750 --> 00:19:12,050
Are you alright?

163
00:19:19,150 --> 00:19:20,750
Come on, get up!

164
00:19:20,850 --> 00:19:22,550
I said get up!
- No, no ...

165
00:19:22,600 --> 00:19:24,750
Now, I don't want to hear yer talk.
Get in the yard.

166
00:19:24,850 --> 00:19:27,200
No, I'm not sure...
- Ain't no need for all that.

167
00:19:27,300 --> 00:19:29,750
Just go on a short trip,
That's all.

168
00:19:29,850 --> 00:19:33,300
Don't want to frighten the children
none over a li'l boat ride, do yah?

169
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:36,200
John's massa gunna pay his debt.
John's massa gunna come for him.

170
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:46,900
I do not want to hear a word,
out of none a yah.

171
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:49,500
Not a word.

172
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,400
No!

173
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:04,000
Okay, let's go!

174
00:20:05,300 --> 00:20:07,900
Come on!

175
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:09,450
Come on child, come on.

176
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:18,050
Come on, move it!

177
00:20:18,150 --> 00:20:20,300
Come on, come on!
Up, up the stairs.

178
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:22,150
Hit it!

179
00:20:22,250 --> 00:20:24,750
Come on, let's go.

180
00:20:26,150 --> 00:20:28,300
Get up!

181
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:29,950
Come on, move it!

182
00:20:30,050 --> 00:20:32,250
Okay, let's go!
- Move it boy!

183
00:20:32,350 --> 00:20:33,500
Take him down!

184
00:20:33,550 --> 00:20:36,055
Hey, you! Come on, get up!

185
00:20:36,150 --> 00:20:39,150
Get down, right there.

186
00:20:40,300 --> 00:20:42,300
Come on.

187
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:46,000
Right there.
Sit down.

188
00:21:20,850 --> 00:21:24,250
Cheer up and don't be so cast down.

189
00:21:33,050 --> 00:21:38,650
If you want to survive,
do and say as little as possible.

190
00:21:38,850 --> 00:21:41,334
Tell no one who you really are,

191
00:21:41,360 --> 00:21:45,125
and tell no one that you
can read and write.

192
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:49,000
Unless you want to be a dead nigger.

193
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:07,750
Now, keep your mouth shut.

194
00:22:13,050 --> 00:22:15,700
I say we fight.

195
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:18,050
The crew is fairly small.

196
00:22:18,150 --> 00:22:20,500
If it were well planned,
I believe they could be strong armed.

197
00:22:20,500 --> 00:22:23,450
Three cant stand against a whole crew.

198
00:22:23,550 --> 00:22:25,850
The rest here are niggers,

199
00:22:25,950 --> 00:22:29,700
born and bred slaves.
Niggers aint got the stomach for a fight.

200
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:33,100
Not a damn one.
- All I know,

201
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:36,950
where we keep travelling
well wish wed died trying.

202
00:22:37,050 --> 00:22:43,850
- Survival is not about certain death,
it is about keeping your head down.

203
00:22:45,100 --> 00:22:49,100
Days ago I was with my family,

204
00:22:49,450 --> 00:22:51,950
In my home.

205
00:22:52,850 --> 00:22:56,050
Now you tell me all is lost.

206
00:22:57,350 --> 00:23:02,350
Tell no one who I really am
if I want to survive.

207
00:23:03,750 --> 00:23:06,950
Well, I dont want to survive,

208
00:23:07,400 --> 00:23:10,100
I want to live.

209
