Better off.
Better than us.

210
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:02,750
I do not see it.
Clemens!

211
00:25:02,850 --> 00:25:04,850
Clemens Ray!

212
00:25:04,950 --> 00:25:07,150
Master Ray, sir!

213
00:25:07,250 --> 00:25:09,450
