Master!

222
00:25:31,700 --> 00:25:32,852
Clemens?
Clemens!

223
00:25:33,500 --> 00:25:36,250
Get back!
- Clemens!

224
00:25:36,350 --> 00:25:38,100
Clemens!

225
00:25:38,200 --> 00:25:40,600
Clemens!

226
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:46,300
Mr. Parker?

227
